Package plan.path.pathfinding

Interface Summary
Heuristics An interface used by the A* Search to implement a number of heuristics, all heuritstics have to satisfy the interface framework
PathFinder An interface which makes it possible for a robot to find a path from one point on the tile map to another one based on that tile map.
Robot A robot interface which will be extended by units
WorldMap Interface used to implement any number of maps, it standardize the all the maps that you can create and use in your calculations.
 

Class Summary
AStar A* Search Algorithm Implementation
Path The data structure that models the Path, it contains a series of steps that has (x,y) coordinates
